jobs_results.title: Senior Mobile Developer
jobs_results.description:
Location: Sandhubel
On behalf of a major client of ours that operates internationally, we are urgently seeking a highly qualified and experienced Mobile Developer. The ideal candidate will be responsible for developing and maintaining innovative mobile applications for iOS and Android platforms. The successful candidate will be integrated into the client’s structure with the possibility of a permanent contract after a probationary period of 6 months.

Your Responsibilities Proven experience in developing mobile applications for iOS and Android.

Familiarity with frameworks including React.js, React Native, and Angular.

Strong UI/UX design skills with a focus on creating user-friendly interfaces.

Ability to work collaboratively in a team environment.

Quick adaptability to new technologies and methodologies.

Fluency in both Italian and English is a fundamental requirement;
German and/or French is a plus.

Degree in Computer Science, Software Engineering, or a related field.

Experience in creating applications connected to web services and APIs.Knowledge of cross-platform application development principles.

Backend computing skills, including database management and frameworks.

Proficiency in programming languages for web development, such as HTML5, CSS, C#, and additional knowledge of Git version control.

Your Perspectives Duration: 6 months (extendable)
Contact & Info Nembrini Consulting SA is an equal opportunity employer and welcomes applications from individuals of all backgrounds and abilities. Given the urgent nature of this search, preference will be given to candidates available for immediate start.
